Author: bruno_guy
Text: i feel the same sometimes, it use to be worse but its gotten better, tbh you just need to find the answer your self try making food that you put a lot of effort in to so you can enjoy it more. or eat out with people or have a meal with people. I know that can be hard because i still can to eat alone and i can only fix food alone and went no one is in the kitchen. But its a process.
